Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.04,0:00:35.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something isn't right.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.25,0:00:39.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've felt someone's eyes\Non me since this morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.54,0:00:45.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody could be out here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.66,0:00:52.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm on a motorcycle\Nin the middle of the open desert.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.33,0:00:56.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who could be following me unseen?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.54,0:00:59.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,There's no way.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.70,0:01:02.29,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be my imagination.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.87,0:01:10.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a sharp one.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.70,0:01:17.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You sensed my presence, a feat even\Nwild bats aren't able to accomplish.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.70,0:01:21.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who the hell are you\Nand why are you tailing me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.78,0:01:23.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not tailing you!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.50,0:01:30.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm capturing you so our army\Ncan ask about Straizo, Joseph Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.66,0:01:34.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Straizo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.84,0:01:36.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Our army?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.41,0:01:51.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,From the silent depths
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.59,0:01:58.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The pillars awaken from ages-long sleep
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.26,0:02:05.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Crimson blood
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.10,0:02:12.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Summons the valorous to stand up
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.98,0:02:20.49,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If inherited love is called fate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.57,0:02:26.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then take another step with smiling eyes
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.46,0:02:33.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Mystify the darkness, dodge in a blink
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.38,0:02:37.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Avoid the blade,\Nfind an opening and strike
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.13,0:02:43.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Conviction tested\Nopens the way to the future
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.35,0:02:47.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Like a bloody storm\NHot like a bloody stone
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.89,0:02:51.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Destiny written into your veins
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.73,0:02:57.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The undying bonds of honor arise
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.53,0:03:02.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take hold of them
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.54,0:03:12.92,Type,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 12: The Pillar Man
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.10,0:03:12.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,By your face and accent,\NI'd say you're German.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.54,0:03:17.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What do you have to do\Nwith Straizo and Speedwagon?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.67,0:03:22.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come on!\NI'll beat some answers out of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.52,0:03:28.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You face the SS commando knife of I,\NDonobang, with your bare hands?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.02,0:03:30.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I feel insulted.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.79,0:03:33.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Come then, stripling!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.23,0:03:36.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Here! Have your flea-ridden\Nmagic carpet back!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.50,0:03:47.28,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-A cactus!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.33,0:03:56.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.25,0:04:01.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You'll need to do better than that\Nto challenge me, you booger!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.68,0:04:07.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, my booger, say,\N"I completely agree, Herr Donobang."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.24,0:04:12.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I completely agree, Herr Donobang.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.68,0:04:15.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's that? I can't hear you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.62,0:04:17.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're a very nimble fellow.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.67,0:04:23.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I wanted to save myself some trouble\Nso I'm lying down here for safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.46,0:04:27.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What? You think you're safe there?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.89,0:04:29.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Have you lost your mind?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.04,0:04:32.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What's with this cactus?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.66,0:04:34.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Take a real close look.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.77,0:04:49.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The cactus was my goal all along!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.83,0:04:55.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cacti are made up of 95% water\Nand conduct Hamon fabulously.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.98,0:04:58.84,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, it's time to talk, Donobang!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.11,0:05:01.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Tell me everything you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.90,0:05:06.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.78,0:05:13.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,When Speedwagon's body disappeared\NI had my hopes, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.62,0:05:16.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He really was safe.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.26,0:05:20.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Well. That's a fine piece of news.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.74,0:05:25.35,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Granny Erina will be\Npleased to hear it.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.72,0:05:31.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But who knows how the Germans\Nare treating him?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.89,0:05:33.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll rescue him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:37.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Then I'll rush home\Nto see Granny Erina's smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.50,0:05:46.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,D-Don't leave me!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.88,0:05:55.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Major von Stroheim,\Nthe pillar is cracking!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.04,0:05:59.17,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It now holds the blood\Nof five prisoners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.17,0:06:01.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The subject's capabilities are unknown.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.83,0:06:05.42,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NFeeding it too much may be dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.41,0:06:10.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How was the blood extracted?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.80,0:06:15.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! Don't answer that! I can imagine.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.77,0:06:25.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Speedwagon.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.96,0:06:32.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why so scared?\NAren't you overreacting a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.22,0:06:36.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be too proud! He's dangerous!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.78,0:06:38.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.64,0:06:40.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That room is a bunker.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.63,0:06:44.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Its iron walls are 50 cm thick!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.75,0:06:49.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It is equipped with flamethrowers,\Nmachine guns and time bombs.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.63,0:06:55.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What child fears a grizzly\Nin a cage at the zoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.51,0:06:57.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,None at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.27,0:07:04.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I believe he's nothing more than a\Ncheap caveman who's lived too long!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.28,0:07:09.70,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Something's spraying out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.28,0:07:13.62,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's blood!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.62,0:07:16.32,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,The blood it absorbed\Nis pouring out!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.32,0:07:17.80,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,We can't see a thing!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.80,0:07:19.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Use the sprinkler system!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.17,0:07:50.78,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His outer layer is taking on\Na flesh-like color and luster!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.03,0:07:54.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's alive! He looks human!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.91,0:08:00.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He needs a name.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.61,0:08:03.04,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\N"The Pillar Man" is awkward to use.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.67,0:08:07.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I, Stroheim, will be his godfather!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.63,0:08:09.33,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Let me think.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.33,0:08:14.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'll name him after the\NMexican sirocco! Santviento!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.81,0:08:19.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's standing!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.18,0:08:21.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Stand up for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.02,0:08:27.31,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Show us what you are made of, Santviento!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.86,0:09:13.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at that! Our Santviento\Nis quite the comedian, isn't he?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.03,0:09:18.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The ultimate organism?!\NWhat's ultimate?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.79,0:09:20.89,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Behold, Speedwagon!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.89,0:09:25.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's sniffing around like\Na man barely out of the trees!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.52,0:09:27.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he has much brains?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.09,0:09:32.01,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is a farce!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.01,0:09:35.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Whatever. Let's say he made the masks.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.88,0:09:38.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You, begin the experiment.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.51,0:09:40.76,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\NOpen the door to the next chamber.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.76,0:09:41.51,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.74,0:09:51.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What is that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.90,0:09:55.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A prisoner.\NA prisoner with a mask, that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-A vampire?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.69,0:10:03.95,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A few days ago, he was a feeble,\Ntoothless old man on death's door.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.08,0:10:08.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't fed him today, \Nso he must be thirsty.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.07,0:10:09.79,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,He'll attack quickly.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:10.00,0:10:13.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,How will they perform?\NLet's watch and see!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.48,0:10:21.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's this? What a surprise!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.09,0:10:23.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he just an ordinary man?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.66,0:10:26.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We have no other subjects to test!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.23,0:10:30.82,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shall we use the explosives planted in
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.82,0:10:33.51,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,\Nthe prisoner's head, Major von Stroheim?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.51,0:10:34.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Major?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.45,0:10:36.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very well. Do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.91,0:10:48.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-Wait! Belay that order!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.80,0:10:52.13,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His jaw. L-Look at his lower jaw!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.13,0:10:57.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-And his arms. Look! Look at his arms!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.62,0:11:00.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I thought he was losing the fight,\Nbut Santviento is absorbing the prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.56,0:11:12.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He is pulling him into his body.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.45,0:11:14.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's eating the prisoner!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.40,0:11:20.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a fantastic creature!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.00,0:11:22.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The masked man is his fodder!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.99,0:11:25.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Santviento feeds with his whole body!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.66,0:11:31.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That means he'll take in all of\Nhis prey's energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.29,0:11:37.80,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He ate him! He ate the masked man!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.80,0:11:39.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He ate him!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.97,0:11:43.93,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-And he's grown!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.43,0:11:45.68,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Keep your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.68,0:11:48.43,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Remember he's in a sealed chamber!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.43,0:11:51.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He only gained some weight\Nafter feeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.66,0:11:53.69,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,And his intelligence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.23,0:11:56.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What of his intelligence?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.82,0:11:59.03,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he capable of thought?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.57,0:12:07.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stroheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.91,0:12:10.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?! He spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.45,0:12:12.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He said my name!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.45,0:12:16.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But he shouldn't be able\Nto hear me in there!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.28,0:12:35.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My cactus pal Donobang said this is where\Nthe secret underground facility is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.52,0:12:38.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Speedwagon has to be in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.65,0:12:41.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now, how to get inside?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.78,0:12:49.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Vegetables, canned goods, meat, ham,\Neggs. That's a basket of food.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.64,0:12:54.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,All right. Now we have to frisk you!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.29,0:13:01.85,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't make that face.\NSmile when I frisk you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.85,0:13:03.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Raise your skirts! And smile!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.52,0:13:13.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Go on through!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.38,0:13:14.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.82,0:13:19.98,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I've brought you some tequila.\NIs that all right to bring through?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.08,0:13:27.11,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Put your hands up!\NYou twitch and we shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.09,0:13:30.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why? Why are you panicking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.52,0:13:31.87,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That's a furtive movement!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.20,0:13:33.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.39,0:13:37.79,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hold it! I-I understand! I won't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.13,0:13:41.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Damn! Y-You Germans are too smart!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.14,0:13:43.55,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You saw right through my disguise!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.88,0:13:47.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're nuts! Of course we did!\NWhat a creep!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.92,0:13:52.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No girl in the world is built like\Nsuch an ox, you ox!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.22,0:13:56.56,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Look at yourself\Nwith clearer eyes, moron!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.81,0:13:58.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What was that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.98,0:14:02.86,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hamon!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.74,0:14:08.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, tacos!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.45,0:14:15.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Shoot, that was depressing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.83,0:14:20.21,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I suppose they won't see\Nthrough an army uniform.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.58,0:14:22.09,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.09,0:14:23.63,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.13,0:14:26.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Weren't you watching?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.51,0:14:30.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Major von Stroheim, I was\Nlooking away for a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.47,0:14:34.72,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You were here.\NEveryone was here.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.14,0:14:38.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But nobody saw.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.02,0:14:44.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is no time for refreshments!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.44,0:14:47.74,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It was only a moment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.33,0:14:52.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I only took my eyes off of him\Nfor a few seconds.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.39,0:14:57.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,My vision is perfect, but I couldn't\Nsee what was happening inside!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.75,0:14:59.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.00,0:15:03.24,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The chamber is sealed!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.24,0:15:05.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But the subject somehow escaped!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.83,0:15:08.34,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The walls show no damage!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.84,0:15:11.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Listen up! Calm down and search for him!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:15.47,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I am sure he's just concealed\Nhimself somewhere!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.16,0:15:20.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Cut off all oxygen!\NWe'll wait for him to come out!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.81,0:15:25.20,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The film record is ready for viewing!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.20,0:15:26.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Show it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.71,0:15:27.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.65,0:15:30.71,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Begin.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.67,0:15:45.67,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's running for the wall!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.09,0:15:47.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.89,0:16:02.66,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's going into the ventilation ducts!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.66,0:16:07.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The entrance is only\Nfour by twenty centimeters!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.30,0:16:11.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,But somehow he's stuffing himself\Ninto that tiny gap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:16.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Incredible! He didn't just\Ndislocate his joints!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.26,0:16:21.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He broke up his own skeleton\Nto twist and alter his shape!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.47,0:16:38.14,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,T-That means he's somewhere\Nin the base's ventilation system!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:43.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,The Pillar Man Santviento spoke your name\Nearlier, Major von Stroheim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.92,0:16:47.15,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He must have heard your name\Nthrough the vents!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.89,0:16:53.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Do the vents lead here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.50,0:16:59.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Soldier! Stand away from that vent!\NYou're in danger!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.31,0:17:14.10,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-It's Santviento!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.13,0:17:21.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Major von Stroheim,\Ndid something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.04,0:17:25.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's so dark! I can't see!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.77,0:17:29.52,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who turned out the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.65,0:17:32.53,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Santviento crawled into the soldier's body!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.36,0:17:36.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Where is everybody?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.36,0:17:40.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Don't leave me here all alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.08,0:17:51.92,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I'm not sure what's going on...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.92,0:17:55.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...but I've never felt so full of life!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.84,0:17:57.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a nightmare.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.34,0:18:02.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If this creature escapes,\Nit will be a dire foe to the Fatherland!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.72,0:18:04.00,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,We must destroy it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.73,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It has to be killed here and now!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.73,0:18:11.48,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Very well! Shoot him!\NBlast that soldier's body to pieces!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:18.45,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That tickles!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.04,0:18:26.46,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's still alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.87,0:18:28.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I knew it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.40,0:18:30.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's immune to bullets!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:35.55,0:18:37.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What a monster!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.10,0:18:45.27,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Why is he pointing?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:47.43,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What's he gonna do?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.69,0:18:51.19,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Wait! Do you think he's\Nmaking a pistol?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.52,0:18:54.44,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Is he imitating us?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.44,0:18:58.04,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-When he spoke, he only said my name.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.04,0:18:59.99,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's mimicking us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.99,0:19:02.41,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It's just mindless aping.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.41,0:19:06.81,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That means he's not intelligent at all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.81,0:19:11.96,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If he's only as smart as a monkey,\Nperhaps we can still use him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.76,0:19:19.40,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.01,0:19:22.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who among you disturbed my slumber?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.93,0:19:24.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,H-He spoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.39,0:19:26.39,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He is capable of thought.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.39,0:19:28.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,A-And his intelligence is great!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.18,0:19:33.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He has learned our speech\Nin this short time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.42,0:19:36.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Die!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.49,0:19:40.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,What the...?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.45,0:19:53.54,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He took a bullet we shot at him\Nand fired it back at us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.54,0:19:56.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man!\NHide over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.50,0:20:00.26,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's still got more bullets to fire!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.26,0:20:04.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,No! I don't need any help\Nfrom a German soldier!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.89,0:20:06.06,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Good heavens.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.74,0:20:10.16,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You never change.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.73,0:20:13.23,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Still stubborn at a time like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.70,0:20:31.25,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I-I can't handle this alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.16,0:20:33.12,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,S-Stay away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.86,0:20:39.05,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, I need some of your hair!\NJust a handful or two!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.05,0:20:41.50,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Yeeowch! What are you doing?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.51,0:20:43.59,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,It'll only hurt for a bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're assaulting an officer!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.47,0:20:47.37,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.85,0:20:49.97,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,That brashness... It couldn't be...!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.67,0:20:56.36,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I call this one Hamon Hair Attack!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.20,0:21:05.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You're... You're...!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.74,0:21:08.91,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Joseph Joestar!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.29,0:21:15.83,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Barrier up!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.48,0:21:40.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,I think you need to start moisturizing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.08,0:21:44.94,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,If you aren't careful, you'll go bald,\NMr. German Army Man.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.94,0:21:47.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,W-When did you get here?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:49.07,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, old man!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:53.95,0:21:55.08,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Ha...ir...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:56.62,0:21:57.75,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Anyhow...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:59.04,0:22:02.30,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,...what a scene I've dropped in on.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.60,0:23:38.60,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Next episode
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.14,0:23:41.65,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,His intelligence is incredible!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.65,0:23:42.90,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,This is horrifying!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.90,0:23:44.77,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Now together, Santviento!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.77,0:23:46.22,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,You primitive.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:46.22,0:23:49.61,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,He's crawling into the wound in my leg!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.61,0:23:52.18,Main,Default,0000,0000,0000,,Chapter 13: JoJo vs.The Ultimate Being
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.18,0:23:54.18,Main,,0000,0000,0000,,
